Lesson 5: Final Touches and Enhancements
Objective:
Add the final touches to make the game engaging.
Introduce mini-games and additional pet actions.
Activities:
Introduce mini-games or shop functionalities.
Allow students to add new images and actions.
Refine the user interface and overall gameplay.
Source Code:
script.js (Add placeholder functions)

javascript
Copy code
// Mini-game and shop placeholders
function visitShop() {
    alert("Welcome to the shop! You can buy food, toys, and medicine for your pet.");
}

function playMiniGame() {
    alert("Starting mini-game... (Coming soon!)");
}
Explanation:
Students can add new functionalities such as shops or mini-games.
Encourage creativity by allowing them to design new features or interactions.
